The product will turn white when diluted with water. When using BERRY CLEAN diluted in water, lightly agitate before each use.


Use: Scrape off excess accumulations of grease, grime and contaminants. Apply BERRY CLEAN to the floor or stain either as a concentrate or at the recommended dilution rate.


Spread uniformly over the surface and allow product to penetrate for approximately 5 minutes. BERRY CLEAN’s unique blend of emulsifiers and wetting agents allow maximum penetration for effective cleaning.


