    'SpecPoxy 3000 (Part A)', 'specpoxy-3000-part-a', 'High-modulus, gel viscosity, moisture-insensitive epoxy adhesive', 'Adhésif époxy à viscosité gélifiée, haute résistance', 'Adhesivo epóxico de alta viscosidad y alta resistencia', 'SpecPoxy 3000 is a two-component, moisture-insensitive, high-modulus, structural epoxy bonding gel. SpecPoxy 3000 is 100% solids, solvent-free, low odor, high strength, and non-sag.', 'Mixing Instructions: Air, material, and surface temperatures must be a minimum of 60°F before mixing or installation. Precondition material to 75°F to assist with mixing and dispensing. For bulk applications, mix equal volumes of Part A and Part B for three minutes using a low-speed drill motor with a Jiffy mixer or paddle. Mix only as much material as can be used within the pot life. For cartridges, the resin and hardener are uniformly dispensed and mixed simultaneously through a mixing nozzleSurface Preparation:  Surfaces to be bonded must be clean and structurally sound. Remove all oil, grease, dirt, laitance, curing compounds, and any other foreign matter by sandblasting, mechanical abrasion, or hydro-blasting. Clean drilled holes with a nylon brush to remove all dust and loose material. Use clean, oil-free compressed air to blow out any remaining water, dust, or debris before application. Ensure bolts, rebar, or threaded rods are free of dirt, grease, or oil.Bonding: As a structural adhesive, apply SpecPoxy 3000 neat and work into the substrate. The glue line should not exceed 1/8”.Anchoring:  For anchoring dowels, bolts, or reinforcing steel, the hole depth should be approximately nine times the bolt diameter. Ensure the hole is properly prepared, drilled, brushed, and blown out before preparing the epoxy. Dispense into a disposable container until a uniform grey is achieved with no streaks.Into Concrete: Dispense the material from the bottom of the hole, filling approximately 5/8 of the hole depth while slowly withdrawing the nozzle. Insert the bolt or dowel by turning it slowly during insertion. Ensure the hole is completely filled with SpecPoxy 3000 and devoid of air pockets or voidsInto Hollow Block:  Completely fill the screen while withdrawing the nozzle. Insert the epoxy-filled screen into the hole and insert the threaded rod to the bottom of the screen while turning slightly clockwise. Do not disturb or bolt up until cured.
Meets ASTM C881 standards, VOC content = 0 g/L.', NULL, NULL, 'When stored in the original, tightly closed container, preventing the accumulation of water, dirt, or other contaminants, the shelf life is two years from the date of manufacture.', 'Always test a small amount of SpecPoxy 3000 to verify that the product has been thoroughly mixed and will harden properly before proceeding. Do not thin with any solvent. Surface and air temperatures must be a minimum of 60°F for application. Avoid hazards by following all precautions found in the Safety Data Sheets (SDS), product labels, and technical literature.', 'Warning', '<p>Calcium Carbonate, 4-Nonylphenol, Bisphenol A Diglycidyl Ether Resin</p>', 'Causes skin irritation. May cause an allergic skin reaction. Causes serious eye irritation. Toxic to aquatic life with long-lasting effects.', 'Wear protective gloves, eye protection, and face protection. Wash thoroughly after handling. Avoid breathing dust/fume/gas/mist/vapors/spray. Contaminated clothing should not be allowed out of the workplace. Avoid release to the environment.', NULL, 'IF ON SKIN: Wash with water. IF IN EYES: Rinse cautiously with water for several minutes. Remove contact lenses if present and easy to do.', 'Store locked up.', 'Dispose of contents/container in accordance with local/regional/national/international regulations.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Not regulated', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/specchem-pwa-feb-25.firebasestorage.app/o/pictograms%2Fgreen-conscious.png?alt=media&token=f58533a5-5698-4e4e-968b-cd4af2bc2a28', 'https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/specchem-pwa-feb-25.firebasestorage.app/o/pictograms%2Fdo-not-freeze.png?alt=media&token=010ba974-dde9-4be7-b80e-5d1f7e7d0e49', NULL, '2 Years', NULL, NULL, 'VOC content= 0 grams/liter',
