ermit maximum penetration.  As jobsite conditions vary, a test panel should always be performed.', NULL, NULL, 'Shelf life of CURE HARD CLEAR in the original tightly closed containers is two years from the date of manufacture. Do not allow accumulation of water, dirt or other contaminants.', 'Protect from freezing. If the surface is to be treated with a glue, coating or paint, excess CURE HARD CLEAR residue must be completely removed. Avoid contact with glass, aluminum, or other glazed or finished surfaces. When contact is encountered, immediately wipe with a damp cloth or flush with water. Do not use on cinder block or other highly porous material containing holes or air pockets.', 'Danger', 'Sodium Silicate', 'Harmful if swallowed. Causes severe skin burns.', 'Do not breathe dust or mist. Wash skin thoroughly after handling. Do not eat, drink, or smoke when using this product. Wear protective gloves/protective clothing/eye protection/face protection.', NULL, 'If in eyes: Rinse with water for several minutes. Remove contact lenses if present and easy to do. Continue rinsing. If irritation persists, seek medical attention.', 'Store locked up.', 'Dispose of contents/container in accordance with local/regional/national/international regulations.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Not regulated', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/specchem-pwa-feb-25.firebasestorage.app/o/pictograms%2Fgreen-conscious.png?alt=media&token=1337ae3b-9ed9-4956-8d2f-fc958810c039', 'https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/specchem-pwa-feb-25.firebasestorage.app/o/pictograms%2Fdo-not-freeze.png?alt=media&token=20c12d11-97d2-4863-999c-3a0e08ccfee4', NULL, '2 years', NULL, NULL, 'Actual VOC = 0g/l',
