s, the shelf life is two years from the date of manufacture. Do not allow to freeze.', 'Protect from freezing. If the surface is to be treated with a glue, coating, or paint, excess Cure Hard Plus residue must be completely removed. Avoid contact with glass, aluminum, or other glazed or finished surfaces. Where contact has occurred, immediately wipe with a damp cloth or flush with water. Avoid hazards by following all precautions found in the Safety Data Sheets (SDS), product labels, and technical literature.', 'Danger', 'Sodium Silicate', 'Harmful if swallowed. Causes severe skin burns.', 'Do not breathe dust or mist. Wash skin thoroughly after handling. Do not eat, drink, or smoke when using this product. Wear protective gloves/protective clothing/eye protection/face protection.', NULL, 'If in eyes: Rinse cautiously with water. If irritation persists, seek medical advice. If swallowed: Call poison center/doctor. Do not induce vomiting.', 'Store locked up.', 'Dispose of contents/container in accordance with local/regional/national/international regulations.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Not regulated', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', NULL, 'https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/specchem-pwa-feb-25.firebasestorage.app/o/pictograms%2Fdo-not-freeze.png?alt=media&token=20c12d11-97d2-4863-999c-3a0e08ccfee4', NULL, '2 years', NULL, NULL, NULL,
