    'Deco Liquid Release', 'deco-liquid-release', 'Liquid release agent for decorative texturing mats', 'Agent de démoulage liquide pour matrices de texturation décoratives', 'Agente desmoldante líquido para moldes texturizantes decorativos', 'DECO LIQUID RELEASE is a colorless liquid release formulated and recommended for use with decorative, mat-type concrete, texturing mats. It forms a lubricating barrier that prolongs the life of the imprinting tools by decreasing the friction between the mats and the concrete.


DECO LIQUID RELEASE is used in the texturing process of both colored and uncolored concrete. It is also used as an alternative to powdered release agents that may not be desired in certain circumstances, such as interior projects.', 'Trowel and finish newly poured concrete surfaces in preparation for the imprinting process. When the concrete has reached the plastic stage desirable for imprinting, DECO LIQUID RELEASE should be used between the texture mats and the concrete to prevent sticking and concrete build up.


Apply in temperatures between 55°F and 80°F. Using a pump-type sprayer, liberally apply a mist of DECO LIQUID RELEASE on the texturing mats AND on the concrete surface, but only on the area where you are going to place the next few mats. Apply over an area of approximately 10 to 15 square feet to avoid evaporation before the mat placements are made, especially on dry windy days.


COVERAGE
