Do not allow repairs to freeze until the materials reach a minimum strength of 1000 psi compressive strength.
Do not apply in areas that will be subject to standing water, immersion, or ambient temperatures below 40°F. 50°F is the intended work area temperature. For subfreezing applications, condition material to between 65°F and 85°F.
Caution: Contains Portland Cement and Calcium Oxide. Contact with water will release alkali which can cause burns. Dust from this product may irritate respiratory system. Read the Safety Data Sheet before use.', 'Danger', 'Crystalline Silica (Quartz)/Silica Sand, Portland Cement, Calcium Oxide, Aluminum Sulfate', 'Suspected of causing cancer. May cause damage to organs (respiratory system) through prolonged or repeated exposure. May cause respiratory irritation. Causes skin irritation. May cause an allergic skin reaction. Causes serious eye damage.', 'Obtain special instructions before use. Do not handle until all safety precautions have been read and understood. Do not breathe dust/fume/gas/mist/vapors/spray. Wash thoroughly after handling. Use only outdoors or in a well-ventilated area. Wear protective gloves/protective clothing/eye protection/face protection. If exposed or concerned: Get medical advice/attention. If skin irritation or rash occurs: Get medical advice/attention. If inhaled: Remove person to fresh air and keep comfortable for breathing. If in eyes: Rinse cautiously with water for several minutes. Remove contact lenses, if present and easy to do. Continue rinsing. If eye irritation persists: Get medical advice/attention. Take off contaminated clothing and wash before reuse.', NULL, 'If inhaled, move to fresh air. If on skin, wash with water. Get medical advice if irritation or rash occurs.', 'Store in a well-ventilated place. Keep container tightly closed.', 'Dispose of contents/container in accordance with local/regional/national/international regulations.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Not regulated', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not regulated', 'https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/specchem-pwa-feb-25.firebasestorage.app/o/pictograms%2Fgreen-conscious.png?alt=media&token=1337ae3b-9ed9-4956-8d2f-fc958810c039', NULL, NULL, '18 Months', NULL, NULL, NULL,
