Corrosion inhibitor for durability', 'Coverage: approx 20 sq ft @ 1/4” per 50 lb bag yields .42 cu ft. Extension with aggregate increases yield.', 'Shelf life of unopened bags stored in a dry facility is 12 months. Excessive temperature differential and/or high humidity can shorten the shelf life expectancy. Store in a cool, dry area away from direct sunlight.', 'Minimum thickness for horizontal repairs subjected to traffic is 1”

