    'SC Cure 500', 'sc-cure-500', 'Concrete Curing Compound', 'Produit de cure pour béton', 'Compuesto para curado de concreto', 'SC CURE 500® is a leading edge technology, concrete curing compound that was developed to cure hard-troweled concrete to be treated with lithium silicate hardeners/denifiers like LITHSEAL. SC CURE 500® penetrates and forms a temporary membrane to cure, densify, harden and dustproof concrete essential for proper strength development. Should SC CURE 500® be over applied or left to dry on the surface of hard-trowel concrete surfaces, the surface membrane becomes brittle and is easily removed with a stiff broom or light abrasion. Once the surface has been cleaned, lithium hardeners can be applied within 7 days. May contribute to LEED credits.', 'COVERAGE: Curing, Sealing, Hardening and Dustproofing:
Hard Troweled Finish: 500-800 sq ft/gal
Broom or Float Finish: 300-400 sq ft/gal
Vertical Surface: 400-500 sq ft/gal
