    'SC MT Black Pigment', 'sc-mt-black-pigment', 'Concentrated carbon black pigment', 'Pigment noir de carbone concentré', 'Pigmento negro concentrado', 'SC-MT BLACK PIGMENT is a concentrated carbon black (lampblack) pigment expressly manufactured for mixing into SC Microtrenching Grout or SC Microtrenching Mortar to better match the surrounding pavement. SC-MT BLACK PIGMENT is treated with dispersing agents and added moisture so that it readily mixes in for maximum color power. SC-MT BLACK PIGMENT is stable to sunlight and UV radiation, alkali resistant, and contains no calcium sulfate.', 'Dosage: Approximately 4 oz. of SC-MT BLACK PIGMENT should be mixed with 100 lbs of the SC Microtrenching Grout. The batch size will depend on the capacity of the contractor''s mixing and pumping equipment.The required water, powder, and pigment should be added to the mixer in this order. Once all the materials have been added, mix thoroughly for a minimum of 3 minutes until a uniform, lump-free consistency is achieved.The dosage of the SC-MT BLACK PIGMENT can be adjusted as needed to better match the surrounding asphalt pavement surface.
Mix 4 oz per 100 lbs of grout to match surrounding pavement.', NULL, NULL, 'Shelf life is 2 years when properly stored in the original sealed container.', 'Weather resistance is good; however, carbon black can migrate in one to four years unless protected from water exposure and evaporation. Sealing concrete surfaces or using a high-strength mix to reduce water permeability can eliminate this effect.DO NOT EXPOSE TO OR APPLY NEAR SPARKS OR FLAMES. FOR WELL-VENTILATED OR EXTERIOR USE ONLY!', 'Warning', '<p>Carbon Black</p>', 'May form combustible dust concentration in air.', 'Not applicable.', NULL, 'None applicable.', 'Store in a well-ventilated place. Keep the container tightly closed.', 'Dispose of contents/container in accordance with local/regional/national/international regulations.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Not regulated', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/specchem-pwa-feb-25.firebasestorage.app/o/pictograms%2Fgreen-conscious.png?alt=media&token=1337ae3b-9ed9-4956-8d2f-fc958810c039', NULL, NULL, '2 years', NULL, NULL, NULL,
