    category_id, sort_order, is_active
  ) VALUES (
    'SC Multi-Purpose Sealer', 'sc-multi-purpose-sealer', 'Clear Non-yellowing Water-based Acrylic Sealer', 'Scellant acrylique à base d''eau, transparent et non jaunissant', 'Sellador acrílico transparente a base de agua, no amarillea', 'SC Multi-Purpose Sealer is a clear, water-based, non-yellowing acrylic sealer developed to beautify and protect a wide variety of interior and exterior surfaces. Applications ranging from decorative concrete, pavers, exposed aggregate, and natural stone, to brick, quarry tile, terrazzo, and more will benefit from this durable, long lasting, easy-to-apply formula. This film-forming, low odor, multi-purpose sealer improves the appearance of all treated surfaces with a medium gloss, satin sheen.
SC Multi-Purpose Sealer protects surfaces from the damaging effects of de-icing salts, and acts as a binder to minimize aggregate pop out. It also provides stain resistance against water, oil, grease and acids on interior and exterior surfaces, and seals interlocking pavers and brick pavers, locking sand in place. The ultimate low VOC multi-purpose sealer for a wide range of applications.', 'Ready-to-use. Do not dilute. Application temperature above 40°F & rising is recommended.
New concrete/Exposed aggregate sealer: Apply with a sprayer, or roller in a uniform thin film; spray apply for best results. Only one coat of SC Multi-Purpose Sealer is needed to cure, seal, beautify, and protect.
For increased gloss, a second coat may be applied. Allow the first coat to thoroughly dry before the second coat is applied, typically 6-8 hours. Two thin coats will produce a better gloss than one heavy coat, especially on porous substrates.
Existing Concrete: Concrete surface must be clean, dry, and free of all stains, oil, grease, dirt, and incompatible coatings prior to application.', NULL, NULL, 'The shelf life of SC Multi-Purpose Sealer in the original tightly closed containers is two years from the date of manufacture. Do not allow the accumulation of water, dirt, or other contaminants.', '- Protect from freezing.- If the surface is to be treated with glue, coating, or paint, excess SC Multi-Purpose Sealer residue must be completely removed.- Avoid contact with glass, aluminum, or other glazed or finished surfaces. If contact occurs, immediately wipe with a damp cloth or flush with water.- Do not use on cinder block or other highly porous material containing holes or air pockets.', 'Warning', '<p>Oleic Acid</p>', 'Causes eye irritation.', 'Wash thoroughly after handling.', NULL, 'IF IN EYES: Rinse with water for several minutes. If irritation persists, get medical attention.', 'None applicable.', 'Dispose of contents/container in accordance with local/regional/national/international regulations.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Not regulated', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', NULL, 'https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/specchem-pwa-feb-25.firebasestorage.app/o/pictograms%2Fdo-not-freeze.png?alt=media&token=20c12d11-97d2-4863-999c-3a0e08ccfee4', NULL, '2 years', NULL, NULL, 'VOC Content: Less than 100 g/L. Complies with Federal VOC standards for Curing and Sealing compounds.',
