Add pre-washed 3/8" pea gravel for deep applicationsmix in two steps for best consistency.', NULL, NULL, 'Store SC Precision Grout in a cool, dry area, away from moisture, rain, or snow. When stored in its original, tightly closed container, the shelf life is one year from the date of manufacture.', '- DO NOT place at temperatures below 40°F (5°C) unless special provisions are followed.- DO NOT mix for more than 5 minutes.- DO NOT overwater or retemper.- Avoid adding cement, sand, or admixtures.Follow all precautions in the Safety Data Sheets (SDS), product labels, and technical literature.', 'Danger', '<p>Crystalline Silica (Quartz)/Silica Sand, Portland Cement, Calcium Oxide, Calcium Aluminate Cement</p>', 'Suspected of causing cancer. May cause damage to organs (Respiratory System) through prolonged or repeated exposure. May cause respiratory irritation. Causes skin irritation. May cause an allergic skin reaction. Causes serious eye damage.', 'Obtain special instructions before use. Do not handle until all safety precautions have been read and understood. Do not breathe dust/fume/gas/mist/vapors/spray. Wash thoroughly after handling. Use only outdoors or in a well-ventilated area. Contaminated work clothing should not be allowed out of the workplace. Do not eat, drink, or smoke when using this product. Wear protective gloves/eye protection/face protection.', NULL, 'IF INHALED: Remove to fresh air. IF ON SKIN: Wash with plenty of water. IF IN EYES: Rinse with water and call a doctor immediately.', 'Store in a well-ventilated place. Keep container tightly closed. Store locked up.', 'Dispose of contents/container in accordance with local/regional/national/international regulations.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Not regulated', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/specchem-pwa-feb-25.firebasestorage.app/o/pictograms%2Fgreen-conscious.png?alt=media&token=1337ae3b-9ed9-