    'Solvent 100', 'solvent-100', 'High strength solvent and cleaner', 'Solvant et nettoyant haute résistance', 'Solvente y limpiador de alta resistencia', 'A clear, colorless, high-strength solvent formulated specifically as a thinner and clean-up material for resin-based compounds.Actual/Maximum VOC Content = 874 grams/liter.', '- For equipment and tool clean-up.- For clean-up of epoxy and urethane on equipment and tools.- Troweling aid for epoxy mortars.- A thinner and clean-up material for acrylic and other resin-based curing compounds.
