 air pockets or voids. Do not disturb or bolt up until curedInto Hollow Block:  Completely fill the screen while withdrawing the nozzle. Insert the epoxy-filled screen into the hole. Insert the threaded rod to the bottom of the screen while turning slightly clockwise. Do not disturb or bolt up until cured.
Meets ASTM C881 standards, VOC content = 0 g/L.', NULL, NULL, 'When stored in the original, tightly closed container, the shelf life is two years from the date of manufacture.', 'Always test a small amount of SpecPoxy 3000 FS to verify that the product has been thoroughly mixed and will harden properly before proceeding. Do not thin with any solvent. Surface and air temperatures must be a minimum of 60°F for application. Follow all precautions found in the Safety Data Sheets (SDS), product labels, and technical literature.', 'Warning', '<p>Bisphenol A Diglycidyl Ether Resin, Calcium Carbonate</p>', 'Causes skin irritation. May cause an allergic skin reaction. Causes serious eye irritation. Toxic to aquatic life with long-lasting effects.', 'Wear protective gloves/eye protection/face protection. Wash thoroughly after handling. Avoid breathing dust/fume/gas/mist/vapors/spray. Contaminated clothing should not be allowed out of the workplace. Avoid release to the environment.', NULL, 'IF ON SKIN: Wash with water. IF IN EYES: Rinse cautiously with water for several minutes. Remove contact lenses if present and easy to do. If irritation persists, get medical attention.', 'Store locked up.', 'Dispose of contents/container in accordance with local/regional/national/international regulations.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Not regulated', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', 'Not applicable', '<img width="72" style="width:72px;object-fit:contain;" src=https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/specchem-pwa-feb-25.firebasestorage.app/o/pictograms%2Fgreen-conscious.png?alt=media&token=1337ae3b-9ed9-4956-8d2f-fc958810c039 class="green-conscious-icon" alt="Green Conscious"/>', '<img width="75" height="75" style="width:75px;height:75px;object-fit:contain;" src=https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/specchem-pwa-feb-25.firebasestorage.app/o/pictograms%2Fdo-not-freeze.png?alt=media&token=20c12d11-97d2-4863-999c-3a0e08ccfee4 alt="Do Not Fre