    'Surface Shine', 'surface-shine', 'High-gloss acrylic sealer (ASTM C-1315 Class A)', 'Scellant acrylique à haute brillance (ASTM C-1315 Classe A)', 'Sellador acrílico de alto brillo (ASTM C-1315 Clase A)', 'SURFACE SHINE is a transparent, high-gloss, non-yellowing acrylic polymer engineered as a cure and seal specifically for exterior surfaces such as exposed aggregate, natural stone, brick, quarry tile, terrazzo, and other concrete surfaces. It is also suitable for interior applications. This non-yellowing, durable sealer enhances the appearance of all treated surfaces with a high-gloss sheen.

