    'V Form Release #1', 'v-form-release-1', 'Mineral oil-based reactive form release agent', 'Agent de décoffrage réactif à base d''huile minérale', 'Agente desmoldante reactivo a base de aceite mineral', 'V Form Release #1 is a mineral oil-base, reactive release agent specially engineered to positively prevent bonding of the concrete to forms and form liners. V Form Release #1 contains no waxes or silicones.
