    'Dry-Deck WB', 'dry-deck-wb', 'DRY-DECK WB is a water-based deck coating system designed specifically for pedestrian deck applications over occupied spaces. This premium coating provides excellent waterproofing protection while mai...', NULL, NULL, 'DRY-DECK WB is a water-based deck coating system designed specifically for pedestrian deck applications over occupied spaces. This premium coating provides excellent waterproofing protection while maintaining a durable, slip-resistant surface suitable for foot traffic.
