- Allow 24-48 hours for full cure', NULL, '40-60 sq ft per gallon', 'Store in original containers between 40°F and 90°F. Protect from freezing. The shelf life of properly stored DRY-DECK WB is one year from the date of manufacture.', 'Not suitable for vehicular traffic or high-impact areas. Do not apply over existing coatings unless properly tested for compatibility. Substrate moisture content should not exceed 4%. Protect from foot traffic during cure period. INDUSTRIAL USE ONLY.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL,
