    'SpecFlow', 'specflow', 'SPECFLOW is a high-performance concrete flowing and leveling agent designed to improve concrete workability and finish quality. This advanced additive reduces the water-cement ratio while increasing f...', NULL, NULL, 'SPECFLOW is a high-performance concrete flowing and leveling agent designed to improve concrete workability and finish quality. This advanced additive reduces the water-cement ratio while increasing flowability, resulting in stronger, more durable concrete with superior surface characteristics.
- Improves concrete flowability and workability
- Reduces water-cement ratio
- Enhances surface finish quality
- Increases concrete strength and durability
- Reduces bleeding and segregation
- Compatible with most concrete admixtures', 'Add SPECFLOW to the concrete mix during the batching process. It can be added directly to the concrete mixer or dissolved in mix water. Add SPECFLOW during concrete mixing for uniform distribution. Mix thoroughly for minimum 2-3 minutes after addition. Place concrete within normal working time. Higher dosage rates may be required for self-leveling concrete applications.', 'Improves concrete flowability and workability, Reduces water-cement ratio, Enhances surface finish quality, Increases concrete strength and durability, Reduces bleeding and segregation, Compatible with most concrete admixtures', 'Dosage rates typically range from 6-16 oz per 100 lbs of cement depending on desired flow characteristics and ambient conditions. For self-leveling applications: 8-20 oz per 100 lbs of cement.', 'Store in original containers in a cool, dry place. Protect from freezing. The shelf life of properly stored SPECFLOW is one year from the date of manufacture.', 'Do not exceed recommended dosage rates as this may cause excessive retardation or bleeding. Not recommended for use in concrete exposed to freeze-thaw conditions unless proper air entrainment is maintained. SPECFLOW may slightly retard set time - adjust project scheduling accordingly. Do not use in concrete containing reactive aggregates without testing. INDUSTRIAL USE ONLY.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Store in dry conditions. Keep container tightly closed. Protect from moisture and freezing.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL,
