    'SpecHard Intraseal', 'spechard-intraseal', 'Penetrating concrete hardener densifier and sealer system', NULL, NULL, 'SPEC HARD-INTRASEAL is a penetrating concrete hardener densifier and sealer designed to increase surface hardness reduce dusting and provide long-term protection for concrete floors. This advanced silicate-based system chemically reacts with concrete to create a harder more durable surface.', 'Surface must be clean and free of all sealers coatings curing compounds and contaminants. Mechanically prepare surface if necessary to ensure penetration. Apply using low-pressure spray or microfiber applicator. Work material into surface ensuring complete coverage. Allow to penetrate fully. Remove excess material before it dries on surface.', 'Penetrating hardener and densifier, Increases surface hardness and abrasion resistance, Reduces dusting and chalking, Chemical reaction with concrete, Permanent improvement to concrete, Easy application, Environmentally safe, No VOCs', 'Approximately 150-300 square feet per gallon depending on concrete porosity and age.', 'Store in original containers in cool dry area. Protect from freezing. Shelf life is 2 years from date of manufacture when properly stored.', 'Not effective on sealed or dense concrete surfaces. Multiple applications may be required for desired results. Surface must be completely clean for proper penetration. Allow adequate time between coats. INDUSTRIAL USE ONLY.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Store in cool dry area between 35°F and 100°F. Do not freeze. Keep container tightly closed.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL,
