    'SpecRock', 'specrock', 'Premium concrete and masonry sealer with excellent water repellency', NULL, NULL, 'SPEC ROCK is a premium concrete and masonry sealer designed to provide excellent water repellency and stain resistance while maintaining surface breathability. This penetrating sealer forms a protective barrier that helps prevent water damage freeze-thaw damage and chemical attack.', 'Surface must be clean and dry. Remove all dirt debris efflorescence previous sealers and contaminants. Allow new concrete to cure for minimum 28 days. Apply using low-pressure spray brush or roller. Apply to saturation maintaining wet edge. Remove any excess material before it dries.', 'Deep penetrating protection, Excellent water repellency, Maintains surface breathability, Stain resistant, UV stable, Long-lasting protection, Does not alter surface appearance, Easy application', 'Approximately 150-300 square feet per gallon depending on surface porosity and texture.', 'Store in original containers in cool dry location. Shelf life is 2 years from date of manufacture when properly stored.', 'Not recommended for surfaces that will be painted or receive other coatings. Test small area first. Do not thin or dilute. Protect surrounding vegetation and vehicles from overspray. Use only in well-ventilated areas. INDUSTRIAL USE ONLY.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Store in cool dry place away from ignition sources. Keep container tightly closed. Store away from oxidizing agents.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL,
