    'SpecShield EX', 'specshield-ex', 'High-performance exempt solvent-based concrete sealer', NULL, NULL, 'SPEC SHIELD EX is a high-performance exempt solvent-based concrete sealer designed for applications requiring low VOC compliance while maintaining superior protection characteristics. This advanced formulation uses exempt solvents to deliver excellent penetration and protection without compromising environmental compliance.', 'Surface must be clean dry and free of contaminants. Remove all dirt oil grease previous sealers curing compounds and loose material. Allow new concrete to cure for minimum 28 days. Apply using brush roller or spray equipment. Work to saturation maintaining wet edge. Remove excess material that does not penetrate.', 'Exempt solvent-based formulation, Low VOC compliant, Excellent penetration and protection, Superior chemical resistance, UV stable, Does not alter surface appearance significantly, Easy application, Environmentally compliant', 'Approximately 250-400 square feet per gallon depending on surface porosity and texture.', 'Store in original containers in cool dry location. Shelf life is 2 years from date of manufacture when properly stored.', 'Not recommended for interior applications without adequate ventilation. Do not apply over existing sealers without compatibility testing. Test small area first. Use only in well-ventilated areas. INDUSTRIAL USE ONLY.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Store in cool dry place away from ignition sources. Keep container tightly closed. Store away from oxidizing agents.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL,
