    'SpecShot', 'specshot', 'SPECSHOT is a rapid-setting, high-strength shotcrete and concrete repair material designed for pneumatic application in vertical and overhead repairs. This advanced dry-mix material provides excellent...', NULL, NULL, 'SPECSHOT is a rapid-setting, high-strength shotcrete and concrete repair material designed for pneumatic application in vertical and overhead repairs. This advanced dry-mix material provides excellent adhesion, low rebound, and superior durability for structural concrete restoration projects.
- Rapid-setting dry shotcrete mix
