    'SpecSilane 100', 'specsilane-100', 'SPECSILANE 100 is a penetrating silane-based concrete sealer that provides long-lasting protection against water intrusion, chloride penetration, and freeze-thaw damage. This deep-penetrating sealer c...', NULL, NULL, 'SPECSILANE 100 is a penetrating silane-based concrete sealer that provides long-lasting protection against water intrusion, chloride penetration, and freeze-thaw damage. This deep-penetrating sealer chemically reacts with concrete to form a permanent hydrophobic barrier while maintaining the surface''s natural appearance and breathability.
